title: No bluster as Jets prepare to face Brady, Patriots
text: > Sports No bluster as Jets prepare to face Brady, Patriots FILE - In this Aug. 21, 2015, file photo, New York Jets coach Todd Bowles calls for a timeout during an NFL football game against the Atlanta Falcons in East Rutherford, N.J. The Jets travel to Foxborough, and a win Sunday, Oct. 25, over the 5-0 Patriots would establish New York's credentials as a contender. But don't expect any outlandish statements from Bowles or his players. (AP Photo/Peter Morgan, File)
